<HEADLINE>
<P>
SUCCESS STORIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The articles on Gaddi Vasquez ("Gaddi Vasquez: On the Republican Fast Track," 
by Dave Lesher) and the Mexican-American middle class were excellent. It is 
time for a change in stereotypical attitudes toward Hispanics. We have a large 
middle class that people seem to ignore. 
</P>
<P>
JOHN F. MENDEZ 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
